I am rating them 2 stars for customer poor service. I placed an order and was very specific when I said two chicken nachos... one with everything and one with everything but NO CHEESE... I said it more than once to the person taking the order. My coworker picks up the order.. my coworker got hers and  on top of mines it read with a black sharpie "NO CHEESE." When I open it guess what was inside? CHEESEEEE!. I was very specific. I call and complain but the guy on the phone tells me that nachos come with cheese. Obviously I am aware of that and thats why I requested NO CHEESE.  They comply to send me another nachos without cheese. I ask for sour cream and they send me ranch sauce. Like seriously I asked for a simple thing. NO CHEESE. That was all. The man on the phone seemed bothered I was complaining but, it was his mistake. He didn't give the delivery man the directions correctly and by the time I got my food it was super cold. To the person taking orders please pay attention when you take orders. Its not fair. By the way the food taste really good just wish the customer service as good.
